Model: Flux-Fill
（Download：https://huggingface.co/spaces/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-Fill-dev）
Use the corresponding LoRA according to the editing type
（Download：https://huggingface.co/ali-vilab/ACE_Plus/tree/main）

Welcome to use the ACE++ on hugginface and modelscope:
https://modelscope.cn/studios/iic/ACE-Plus
https://huggingface.co/spaces/scepter-studio/ACE-Plus

Upload your object to node ”Reference Image“ and your background image to node ”Edit Image“, Open 'Edit Image' in  Maskeditor and draw the mask(where you choose to place your object.), Choose ACE++Subject LoRA model, Enter prompt words, then click the Queue button!
Examples
Edit image: https://iic-ace-plus.ms.show/file=/tmp/gradio/c3e551a5b4ff8eabaeaf71c08aa13ce32008ccc7f11b7a684bd2acf23c1b5b40/1_1_edit.png

Upload your object image to node ”Edit Image“, Choose ACE++Subject LoRA model, Enter prompt words, then click the Queue button!
Examples

Upload the character you want to keep to the node ”Reference Image“ and the background image to the node ”Edit Image“, Open 'Edit Image' in  Maskeditor and draw the mask(where you choose to swap the face.), Choose ACE++Portrait LoRA model, Enter prompt words, then click the Queue button!
